---
import '../styles/components/sections.css';
---

<section class="section" id="ctf">
  <h2 class="title">CTF Adventures</h2>
  <div class="ctf-content">
    <p class="ctf-description">
      As a passionate CTF player, I'm proud to be part of <span class="name-highlight">CremeTartineFabuleuse</span>, where we tackle challenging puzzles and security scenarios together. My expertise lies particularly in forensics and network challenges, which I also create for <span class="name-highlight">Securinets INSAT</span> events. Through crafting these challenges, I aim to make security learning both engaging and educational for participants.
    </p>
    <div class="ctf-achievements">
      <div class="skill-item">
        <h3>Challenge Creator</h3>
        <p>Specializing in forensics and network security challenges for Securinets INSAT CTF events.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-item">
        <h3>Team Player</h3>
        <p>Active member of CremeTartineFabuleuse, contributing to team victories through technical expertise and collaboration.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="button-container">
      <img src="/images/dog.gif" alt="Animated dog" class="ctf-dog" />
      <div class="buttons">
        <a href="/ctf-events" class="ctf-button">
          View Events
          <span class="button-glow"></span>
        </a
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
